                    <details open>
                        <summary>Seamless booking experience</summary>
                        <p>Let clients browse available time slots, choose their preferred staff member, and book instantly — all from a beautiful, mobile‑friendly interface. No phone calls required.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details>
                        <summary>Relationship-building tools</summary>
                        <p>Send automated confirmations, reminders, and follow‑up messages. Keep a complete client history with notes, so every interaction feels personal and intentional.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details>
                        <summary>Easy and secure client payment options</summary>
                        <p>Accept payments at booking or on‑site. Integrated with major payment providers to process transactions securely, reduce no‑shows with prepayment, and simplify reconciliation.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ln-detail-image reveal-right">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=800&h=640&fit=crop" alt="Client booking experience" loading="lazy" />
